<p>Informatics 45 Spring 2010<br />
   Schedule</p>

</div>

<div class="section">

<hr />

<p>The schedule is a work-in-progress that will be built as we go along, depending on our progress (and, perhaps toward the end, your areas of interest).  I will try to keep the lecture schedule and readings at least a week ahead of us, so you'll know to expect, at least in the short term.</p>

<p>There will sometimes be online readings associated with lectures.  We will generally be talking about them, or about the issues raised in them, in lecture; it's best to do the readings before the lecture, so that you can participate in the discussion and get the most out of your time.</p>

